2. Performs a LEFT JOIN between Projects and Departments (which simulates a RIGHT JOIN between Departments and Projects)
3. Returns a vector of DepProj structs containing department names (optional, since some projects might not have departments) and project names

The `std::optional<std::string>` for department_name handles cases where projects might not be associated with any department (though in a properly designed database, this should be rare).

